Step1: Login with amazon crediantails
Step2: click instances and click new instances then follow steps, storage, port, all module installed like http, https, ssh, mysql etc then create pem file then convert that file to ppk
Step3: open winscp enter host, username(ubuntu) and ppk file and then run below commands to have the necessary modules 
Step:4
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install mysql-server mysql-client
sudo apt-get install apache2
sudo apt-get install php7.0-sqlite3 php7.0-gd php7.0-mysql php7.0-curl php7.0-json php7.0-cgi  php7.0 libapache2-mod-php7.0 php7.0-mbstring php7.0-xml php7.0-zip php7.0-pspell php7.0-intl php7.0-snmp php7.0-mcrypt php7.0-recode php7.0-tidy php7.0-xsl
sudo apt-get install phpmyadmin
sudo a2enmod rewrite
sudo chown -R ubuntu:ubuntu /var/www/html/

: if phpmyadmin not working-
sudo nano /etc/apache2/apache2.conf
add this line:
Include /etc/phpmyadmin/apache.conf
then sudo service apache2 restart